rds: beyond there pluralities (if bodies) he retains a kind of arche‐ in typal incorruptable ultra body or morphosis whch ich 23) neitter changes nor dies. Thus, I feel, I have penetrated to the heart of the mystery which Paul speaks of (\"Behold! I tell you a mystery, etc) + have put the mess ase of the N.T. in specificly modern \"hard fact\" terms! Nearly 4 years after experiencing the revival of an apostolic Xtian in me, + seeing the Logos, I have explicated an overview of how it operates I see another implication of the deliberate setting off of my 2-74/3-74 experience: the true, secret [history - altering] church is, after its stunning victory over the US (etc) tyranay - it is ready now to come out in the open, to \"let it be revealed that it exists + has always existed, for at least 2000 years; + is ready to begin open (visible) battle. This is connects with the coming 2nd advent. This is startlings re me, did is disclose itself to an outsider? No. Via Thomas I am part of it. But I am one who does + will speak openly, + they (it) is/are aware of this. It is this new willingness to surface which explains the \"Encounters of the 3rd kind. esp. the healing ones, + the manipulations of reality + of human minds. It is all this, the true secret church gradually emerging; the Corpus Christi + all its powers + miracles are impinging on us - + my 2-74/3-74 experience is such a one just one of many (to many people). - is it possible that there is a DNA mind, capable, under certain extraordinary conditions (such as acute stress related to problem-solving) of becoming temporarily conscious - within given person? a 25 Put another way. suppose that each of us contains within him a portion of a DNA mind which covertly controls him. of which he is never aware. It programs his every response to every stimulus. Now, suppose that the early Xtians; via Christ, are with him, this unsuspected hidden true mind in each of us or some of us. Then for those persons, for us, we are servants of Christ. However, once that Christ mind breaks through into consciousness, + we learn not only that it is there, but also experience its nature + purpose, we are elevated from servant to friend of Christ I am not sure that this hidden supermind exists in everyone. Maybe He chooses some of us. We so chosen would be so to speak Avatars of Christ but suffering from a purposeful amnesia. Under these circumstances, then, anamnesis is everything (regarding one's identity. + purpose): All Gnosic is a remembering. Which fits My \"we are DNA coils in which memory is stored But no matter how much I can stress the significance of anamnesis correctly, I am still left with the external entity Zebra + its memesis (mimickry). Obviously there is some relationship either between Zebra + anamnesis or at the very lease between being able to perceive ZEBRA + remembering. Now, the Hindo religion teaches that Maya obscures what truly is outside us +, inwardly, manifests itself as amnesia, which is equal to the loss of authentic self (identity). In a sense one is inner + the other outer, but also one concerns time (inner) + space (outer). The ajna chokra permits an experience of vast reaches of external space + inner time. At the same time reality under‐ goes a perceived transformation, stated briefly, the many are experienced as [the) one: + not as things or thing but a living or quasi-living entelechy or artifact (computer? AI system?). It has a characteristic \"still small\" voice. We may be iso‐ morphic with it mentally (it as psyche or noös) but not isomorphic physically. 95 functionally either it is plugged into us or we into it Now, I say that normally it programs or controls our responses to each situation (stimulus), but without our being aware either of it or its power to delirmine our lives (which seems to be a way, its way, of structuring chaos into order - i.e. harmonie). Only under the most exceptional circumstances does it throw off its mask of con cealment (within our heads) + palpably take control. I can only envision this happening under the unique conditions of the historic bulk of efficient causal proces ses being overruled - which would be (like the eerre intrusions of Runciter + the messages in \"Ubik\") eerie, would tend to promote the realization that the reality as normally experienced is somehow spurious - like The landscape of a dreamer who is either awakening or is being awakened from outside the dream land scape. The value of the novel \"Ubik\" in interpreting my 2-74 3-74 etal experiences lies in a study (cf Lem's article) of the significance of the intrusions for the characters in \"Ubik\" these intrusions do not prove merely that the landscape is spurious, but that (more important) another evidently [more] real landscape exists beyond it which is breaking through with ➀ purposeful signals to us which (2) indicate a sentient + concerned signaler - + thus once again We have the \"ham sandwich\" model of reality 3 7 2 with (1 + (3) isomorphics ts + world t is as an impedement to the reunification of ➀ +",
